 ### In-Scope\\n36: \\n37: | Component | Path | Description |\\n38: |-----------|------|-------------|\\n39: | AgentMetadata | `agentcube/models/agent_models.py` | 新的独立模型文件 |\\n40: | MetadataOptions | `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | 增强的方法 |\\n41: | MetadataService | `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | 新增方法 |\\n42: | Unit tests | `tests/test_metadata_service.py` | 测试覆盖 |\\n43: \\n44: ### Out-of-Scope\\n45: \\n46: - CLI 命令参数变更\\n47: - Runtime 类修改\\n48: - 数据库持久化\\n49: \\n50: ---\\n51: \\n52: ## Impact Analysis\\n53: \\n54: ### Dependencies\\n55: \\n56: | Dependency | Purpose | Status |\\n57: |------------|---------|--------|\\n58: | `pydantic>=2.0.0` | 数据模型验证 | ...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z_logs/AR-025_ST-4.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775866077794,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286223411ffeKbA8FUsl45wcDy\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79dde0e000102bnT5yGGC3f4d\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79ddccdc001lMUytTY80MrbXb\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286223411ffeKbA8FUsl45wcDy\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"glob\",\"callID\":\"toolu_b985e89395b443d093f5f445\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"**/*\"},\"output\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/design.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-025/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/proposal.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/.ruff_cache/0.15.10/16767802250272035660\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/.ruff_cache/0.15.10/9322794169808289981\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/.pytest_cache/v/cache/nodeids\\