*: cli-toolkit/design.md, cli-toolkit/spec.md\\n14: \\n15: ---\\n16: \\n17: ## Background\\n18: \\n19: The MetadataService is responsible for managing agent metadata (agent configuration stored in YAML files) throughout the agent lifecycle: pack, build, publish, invoke, and status operations. This includes loading, saving, updating, and validating metadata based on workspace structure and deployment requirements.\\n20: \\n21: Key components:\\n22: - `AgentMetadata`: Pydantic model for agent configuration\\n23: - `MetadataOptions`: CLI options dataclass for pack operations\\n24: - `MetadataService`: Service class for metadata CRUD operations\\n25: \\n26: ---\\n27: \\n28: ## Requirements\\n29: \\n30: ### Requirement: AgentMetadata model validation\\n31: \\n32: The system SHALL validate `AgentMetadata` fields using Pydantic validators for language, build_mode, and port range.\\n33: \\n34: #### Scenario: Invalid language value\\n35: - **GIVEN** the metadata contains `languag...\n  Line 28: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775866141208,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286223411ffeKbA8FUsl45wcDy\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79de7232001NofOtWli6Ss2io\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79de5a58001pRE28xu7Jl8Yhe\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286223411ffeKbA8FUsl45wcDy\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_0cbe56ce7b874d74bd7debaa\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型 Tasks\\n\\n**Module:** cmd/cli  \\n**Language:** Python  \\n**Size:** M  \\n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Implementation Tasks\\n\\n### Phase 1: AgentMetadata Model Enhancements\\n\\n- [ ] **T001** Review existing `AgentMetadata` Pydantic model in `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\\n  - Verify all fields from design are present\\n  - Confirm validators: `validate_language`, `validate_build_mode`, `validate_port`\\n\\n- [ ] **T002** Write unit tests for `AgentMetadata` validators:\\n  - Test invalid language value raises ValidationError\\n  - Test invalid build_mode value raises ValidationError\\n  - Test port out of range (1-65535) raises ValidationError\\n  - Test language normalization (uppercase to lowercase)\\n\\n- [ ] **T003** Run existing tests to verify current implementation:\\n  - `pytest tests/test_metadata_service.py -v`\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Phase 2: MetadataService Load Operations\\n\\n- [ ] **T010** Verify existing `load_metadata` fallback chain:\\n  - `agent_metadata.yaml` (primary)\\n  - `agent.yaml` (fallback)\\n  - `metadata.yaml` (fallback)\\n\\n- [ ] **T011** Verify error handling:\\n  - Test `FileNotFoundError` when no metadata file exists\\n\\n- [ ] **T012** Run existing load tests to confirm functionality\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Phase 3: MetadataService Save Operations\\n\\n- [ ] **T020** Update `save_metadata` to match YAML formatting requirements:\\n  - Add `indent=2` parameter to `yaml.safe_dump`\\n  - Add `exclude_none=True` to `model_dump(exclude_none=True)`\\n\\n- [ ] **T021** Write test for YAML formatting:\\n  - Verify output uses `default_flow_style=False`, `indent=2`, `sort_keys=False`\\n  - ...\n  Line 31: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775866144497,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286223411ffeKbA8FUsl45wcDy\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79dee2ac001OKA8ACZtz7wVw5\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79deda4900129MLbog4QrXosj\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286223411ffeKbA8FUsl45wcDy\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_67664d4e4e724613ac3b30ca\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-025/tasks.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-025/tasks.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型 Tasks\\n2: \\n3: **Module:** cmd/cli  \\n4: **Language:** Python  \\n5: **Size:** M  \\n6: **Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\\n7: \\n8: ---\\n9: \\n10: ## Implementation Tasks\\n11: \\n12: ### Phase 1: AgentMetadata Model Enhancements\\n13: \\n14: - [ ] **T001** Review existing `AgentMetadata` Pydantic model in `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\\n15:   - Verify all fields from design are present\\n16:   - Confirm validators: `validate_language`, `validate_build_mode`, `validate_port`\\n17: \\n18: - [ ] **T002** Write unit tests for `AgentMetadata` validators:\\n19:   - Test invalid language value raises ValidationError\\n20:   - Test invalid build_mode value raises ValidationError\\n21:   - Test port out of range (1-65535) raises ValidationError\\n22:   - Test language normalization (uppercase to lowercase)\\n23: \\n24: - [ ] **T003** Run existing tests to verify current implementation:\\n25:   - `pytest tests/test_metadata_service.py -v`\\n26: \\n27: ---\\n28: \\n29: ### Phase 2: MetadataService Load Operations\\n30: \\n31: - [ ] **T010** Verify existing `load_metadata` fallback chain:\\n32:   - `agent_metadata.yaml` (primary)\\n33:   - `agent.yaml` (fallback)\\n34:   - `metadata.yaml` (fallback)\\n35: \\n36: - [ ] **T011** Verify error handling:\\n37:   - Test `FileNotFoundError` when no metadata file exists\\n38: \\n39: -...\n  Line 34: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775866151763,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286223411ffeKbA8FUsl45wcDy\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79defa810011240E7xuKsmQfA\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79dee728001JgqkKjprlQZ2dz\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286223411ffeKbA8FUsl45wcDy\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Created `changes/AR-025/tasks.md` with 92 atomic tasks across 10 phases:\\n\\n1. **Phase 1-3**: Review existing implementation + tests for AgentMetadata model, load/save operations\\n2. **Phase 4**: Implement `update_metadata` method (not yet in codebase)\\n3. **Phase 5**: Implement workspace validation for Python/Java\\n4. **Phase 6**: Implement `MetadataOptions.from_options` method\\n5. **Phase 7-8**: Integration with runtimes and providers\\n6. **Phase 9-10**: E2E testing and build verification\