t metadata (agent configuration stored in YAML files) throughout the agent lifecycle: pack, build, publish, invoke, and status operations. This includes loading, saving, updating, and validating metadata based on workspace structure and deployment requirements.\\n\\nKey components:\\n- `AgentMetadata`: Pydantic model for agent configuration\\n- `MetadataOptions`: CLI options dataclass for pack operations\\n- `MetadataService`: Service class for metadata CRUD operations\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Requirements\\n\\n### Requirement: AgentMetadata model validation\\n\\nThe system SHALL validate `AgentMetadata` fields using Pydantic validators for language, build_mode, and port range.\\n\\n#### Scenario: Invalid language value\\n- **GIVEN** the metadata contains `language` set to `\\\"javascript\\\"`\\n- **WHEN** Pydantic validates the model\\n- **THEN** it SHALL raise a `ValidationError` with message indicating allowed values are `['python', 'java']`\\n\\n#### Scenario: Invalid build_mode value\\n- **GIVEN** the metadata contains `build_mode` set to `\\\"hybrid\\\"`\\n- **WHEN** Pydantic validates the model\\n- **THEN** it SHALL raise a `ValidationError` with message indicating allowed values are `['local', 'cloud']`\\n...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z_logs/AR-025_ST-1.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775865709269,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28627d2a7ffecz2E2EsusqJaAu\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79d83d7a001PvugwRJu5w1SAV\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79d82e41001VddTKXgOEVBWao\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28627d2a7ffecz2E2EsusqJaAu\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_99ccd98c7f70420688d454a1\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/.sdd_prompt.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/.sdd_