li_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/proposal.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-022/tasks.md\\n/home/ds...\n  Line 9: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775861190203,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2866cdffeffebbLEVIAe132gIZ\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79934990001hqhT7Rmb2ELPjS\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79933edf001RiI5w9NR1fY3Jv\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2866cdffeffebbLEVIAe132gIZ\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_fbe195e8cb924d649e414b1c\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-025/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-025/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型\\n2: \\n3: **Module:** cmd/cli\\n4: **Language:** Python\\n5: **Size:** M\\n6: \\n7: ## 目的\\n8: \\n9: 为 AgentCube CLI 实现元数据服务层与核心数据模型，提供 workspace 元数据的加载、保存、验证和更新能力，支撑 `pack`、`build`、`publish`、`invoke`、`status` 全生命周期的元数据管理。\\n10: \\n11: 当前 CLI 各 Runtime 类需要读写 workspace 中的 agent 配置信息，但缺乏统一的服务抽象和强类型数据模型。本 AR 在 `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` 中实现 `MetadataService` 类，在 `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` 中定义 `MetadataOptions` dataclass，并使用 Pydantic `BaseModel` 定义 `AgentMetadata` 模型。\\n12: \\n13: ## 范围\\n14: \\n15: ### 包含\\n16: \\n17: 1. **`AgentMetadata` Pydantic 模型**\\n18:    - 定义在 `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`（或独立模块）\\n19:    - 22 个字段覆盖 agent 名称、语言、入口、端口、构建模式、镜像、认证、端点、探针、K8s 部署等\\n20:    - 3 个 validators：`validate_language`（python/java）、`validate_build_mode`（local/cloud）、`validate_port`（1-65535）\\n21:    - 支持 `model_dump(exclude_none=True)` 用于 YAML 序列化\\n22: \\n23: 2. **`MetadataOptions` Dataclass**\\n24:    - 定义在 `agentcube/models/pack_models.py`\\n25:    - 14 个可选字段，接收 CLI 命令行选项\\n26:    - `from_options(cls, options: Dict[str, Any])` 类方法从字典构造\\n27: \\n28: 3. **`MetadataService` 类实现**\\n29:    - `load_metadata(workspace_path)` — 按 `agent_metadata.yaml` → `agent.yaml` → `metadata.yaml` 优先级回退加载\\n30:    - `save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)` — 写入 `agent_metadata.yaml`，使用 `yaml.dump(default_flow_style=False, indent=2,...\n  Line 10: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775861191540,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2866cdffeffebbLEVIAe132gIZ\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79934e9d001iFmKyu1TX2suaV\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79933edf001RiI5w9NR1fY3Jv\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2866cdffeffebbLEVIAe132gIZ\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_614b33aaa30d4aa280fce6e3\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-025/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-025/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型 — Design\\n2: \\n3: ## Overview\\n4: \\n5: This design specifies the full technical implementation of the metadata service layer and core data models for the AgentCube CLI. It covers three components:\\n6: \\n7: 1. **`AgentMetadata`** — Pydantic `BaseModel` with 22 fields, 3 validators (`language`, `build_mode`, `port`), and `model_dump(exclude_none=True)` for YAML serialization.\\n8: 2. **`MetadataOptions`** — dataclass with 14 optional fields and a `from_options()` classmethod for CLI-to-model conversion.\\n9: 3. **`MetadataService`** — service class providing `load_metadata()`, `save_metadata()`, `update_metadata()`, `validate_workspace()`, and language-specific workspace validation.\\n10: \\n11: These components form the foundation for all CLI lifecycle commands (`pack`, `build`, `publish`, `invoke`, `status`) — each Runtime class reads/writes workspace metadata through `MetadataService` rather than direct file I/O.\\n12: \\n13: ---\\n14: \\n15: ## Architecture\\n16: \\n17: ### 2.1 Data Flow\\n18: \\n19: ```\\n20: ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\\n21: │                        CLI Commands (Typer)                           │\\n22: │   pack / build / publish / invoke / status                            │\\n23: └────────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────┘\\n24:    ...\n  Line 11: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775861192915,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2866cdffeffebbLEVIAe132gIZ\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d799353f4001hnViE4vdXOcd0K\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79933edf001RiI5w9NR1fY3Jv\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2866cdffeffebbLEVIAe132gIZ\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_01815a79df634df7bb3606a8\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-025/delta-spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-025/delta-spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-025: MetadataService 与数据模型 — Delta Spec\\n2: \\n3: ## Context\\n4: \\n5: - **Module:** `cmd/cli`\\n6: - **Language:** Python\\n7: - **Size:** M\\n8: - **Base specs:** `cli-toolkit/design.md`, `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\\n9: \\n10: ## Delta Requirements\\n11: \\n12: ### Requirement: AgentMetadata Pydantic model\\n13: \\n14: The system SHALL define `AgentMetadata` as a Pydantic `BaseModel` with typed fields, defaults, descriptions, and validators for language, build_mode, and port.\\n15: \\n16: #### Scenario: Construct with required fields only\\n17: - **GIVEN** input `agent_name=\\\"test-agent\\\"` and `entrypoint=\\\"main.py\\\"`\\n18: - **WHEN** `AgentMetadata(agent_name=\\\"test-agent\\\", entrypoint=\\\"main.py\\\")` is constructed\\n19: - **THEN** the instance SHALL have defaults `language=\\\"python\\\"`, `port=8080`, `build_mode=\\\"local\\\"`, `requirements_file=\\\"requirements.txt\\\"`, `registry_url=\\\"\\\"`, `registry_username=\\\"\\\"`, `registry_password=\\\"\\\"`, and all `Optional` fields as `None`\\n20: \\n21: #### Scenario: Construct with all fields\\n22: - **GIVEN** a complete dict of all `AgentMetadata` fields\\n23: - **WHEN** `AgentMetadata(**fields)` is constructed\\n24: - **THEN** the instance SHALL have all fields set to the provided values\\n25: \\n26: #### Scenario: Required field agent_name missing\\n27: - **GIVEN** no `agent_name` is provided\\n28: - **WHEN** `AgentMetadata...\n  Line 12: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775861194201,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2866cdffeffebbLEVIAe132gIZ\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79935950001dtG11IQ2QlHMqo\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79933edf001RiI5w9NR1fY3Jv\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2866cdffeffebbLEVIAe132gIZ\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_8721fca023e74ee588347722\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-025/tasks.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-025/tasks.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型 — Tasks\\n2: \\n3: > **Module:** cmd/cli\\n4: > **Language:** Python\\n5: > **Size:** M\\n6: > **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\\n7: > **Reference:** `changes/AR-025/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-025/design.md`, `changes/AR-025/delta-spec.md`\\n8: > **Dependency:** None\\n9: \\n10: ## T1. AgentMetadata Pydantic Model — Field Definitions\\n11: \\n12: - [ ] 1.1 Define `AgentMetadata` as a Pydantic `BaseModel` in `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\\n13: - [ ] 1.2 Add 2 required fields: `agent_name: str` (no default), `entrypoint: str` (no default)\\n14: - [ ] 1.3 Add 3 validated fields with defaults: `language: str = \\\"python\\\"`, `port: int = 8080`, `build_mode: str = \\\"local\\\"`\\n15: - [ ] 1.4 Add 4 string-