JavaWorkspace` (pom.xml present, pom.xml missing raises)\\n- Fixed `workspace_with_primary` fixture to include `requirements.txt`\\n- Fixed `TestSaveMetadataFormat` to use nested dict for indentation check\\n\\n**Results:** 51/51 tests pass, ruff clean.\",\"time\":{\"star...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-025_ST-4.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775859825644,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286839261ffe5vMhuvJXyxZ1Bh\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d797c751d001Tc3IZioVdlBwDj\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d797c6e82001BkXPYo64I68e1q\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286839261ffe5vMhuvJXyxZ1Bh\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"task\",\"callID\":\"call_1da250a4ac80488fabd6ce3b\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"description\":\"Explore project structure\",\"prompt\":\"Explore the project at /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z to understand:\\n1. The overall project structure (list top-level directories and key files)\\n2. Look for any existing tasks.md, spec.md, design.md, or similar planning documents\\n3. Look for any existing metadata service or data model related code\\n4. Check if there's a cmd/cli directory or similar Python CLI structure\\n5. Look for any ST-3 stage completion artifacts or documentation\\n6. Find examples of how tasks are structured in this project (if any exist)\\n\\nReturn a comprehensive summary of what you find, including file paths and relevant content snippets.\",\"subagent_type\":\"explore\"},\"output\":\"task_id: ses_286837b3bffeivdSHGNUvWYjLL (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\\n\\n<task_result>\\nHere is a comprehensive summary of the project exploration:\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 1. Overall Project Structure\\n\\n**Root:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z`\\n\\n### Top-Level Directories and Key Files\\n\\n| Entry | Description |\\n|-------|-------------|\\n|