VIbhv2bR5Vjk\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28686b59affeAylUCxRXkYiV1W\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_a3c0b5add0624aee9f23e603\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-025/proposal.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-025/proposal.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型\\n2: \\n3: **Module:** cmd/cli\\n4: **Language:** Python\\n5: **Size:** M\\n6: \\n7: ## 目的\\n8: \\n9: 为 AgentCube CLI 实现元数据服务层与核心数据模型，提供 workspace 元数据的加载、保存、验证和更新能力，支撑 `pack`、`build`、`publish`、`invoke`、`status` 全生命周期的元数据管理。\\n10: \\n11: 当前 CLI 各 Runtime 类需要读写 workspace 中的 agent 配置信息，但缺乏统一的服务抽象和强类型数据模型。本 AR 在 `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` 中实现 `MetadataService` 类，在 `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` 中定义 `MetadataOptions` dataclass，并使用 Pydantic `BaseModel` 定义 `AgentMetadata` 模型。\\n12: \\n13: ## 范围\\n14: \\n15: ### 包含\\n16: \\n17: 1. **`AgentMetadata` Pydantic 模型**\\n18:    - 定义在 `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`（或独立模块）\\n19:    - 22 个字段覆盖 agent 名称、语言、入口、端口、构建模式、镜像、认证、端点、探针、K8s 部署等\\n20:    - 3 个 validators：`validate_language`（python/java）、`validate_build_mode`（local/cloud）、`validate_port`（1-65535）\\n21:    - 支持 `model_dump(exclude_none=True)` 用于 YAML 序列化\\n22: \\n23: 2. **`MetadataOptions` Dataclass**\\n24:    - 定义在 `agentcube/models/pack_models.py`\\n25:    - 14 个可选字段，接收 CLI 命令行选项\\n26:    - `from_options(cls, options: Dict[str, Any])` 类方法从字典构造\\n27: \\n28: 3. **`MetadataService` 类实现**\\n29:    - `load_metadata(workspace_path)` — 按 `agent_metadata.yaml` → `agent.yaml` → `metadata.yaml` 优先级回退加载\\n30:    - `save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)` — 写入 `agent_metadata.yaml`，使用 `yaml.dump(default_flow_style=False, indent=2,...\n  Line 32: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775859664508,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28686b59affeAylUCxRXkYiV1W\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7979fa94001bmqBk61nkargTf\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7979e3c1001kE9uQn9EFzFFfQ\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28686b59affeAylUCxRXkYiV1W\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"call_039747ca39c44e179db28b38\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型 — Design\\n\\n## Overview\\n\\nThis design specifies the full technical implementation of the metadata service layer and core data models for the AgentCube CLI. It covers three components:\\n\\n1. **`AgentMetadata`** — Pydantic `BaseModel` with 22 fields, 3 validators (`language`, `build_mode`, `port`), and `model_dump(exclude_none=True)` for YAML serialization.\\n2. **`MetadataOptions`** — dataclass with 14 optional fields and a `from_options()` classmethod for CLI-to-model conversion.\\n3. **`MetadataService`** — service class providing `load_metadata()`, `save_metadata()`, `update_metadata()`, `validate_workspace()`, and language-specific workspace validation.\\n\\nThese components form the foundation for all CLI lifecycle commands (`pack`, `build`, `publish`, `invoke`, `status`) — each Runtime class reads/writes workspace metadata through `MetadataService` rather than direct file I/O.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Architecture\\n\\n### 2.1 Data Flow\\n\\n```\\n┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\\n│                        CLI Commands (Typer)                           │\\n│   pack / build / publish / invoke / status                            │\\n└────────────────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────┘\\n                             │\\n          ┌──────────────────┴──────────────────┐\\n          ▼                                     ▼\\n┌─────────────────────┐             ┌─────────────────────┐\\n│    Runtime Class    │             │   MetadataOptions   │\\n│  (PackRuntime etc)  │             │   (CLI → dataclass) │\\n│                     │             └──────────┬──────────┘...\n  Line 33: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775859664597,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28686b59affeAylUCxRXkYiV1W\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7979f95e001tK2YZftb8rD707\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7979e3c1001kE9uQn9EFzFFfQ\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28686b59affeAylUCxRXkYiV1W\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Now I have full context. Let me write the comprehensive design.md for AR-025.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775859664595,\"end\":1775859664595}}}\n  Line 40: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775859688746,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28686b59affeAylUCxRXkYiV1W\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d797c5420001OyUq3HYw9wl0WY\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d797c3847001aifTgy491vI2Nq\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28686b59affeAylUCxRXkYiV1W\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"31 of 32 tests pass. The 1 failure (`TestSaveMetadataFormat`) is a pre-existing test issue — it asserts `\\\"  \\\"` (2-space indent) exists in the YAML, but with only top-level fields (no nested dicts), `yaml.dump(indent=2)` produces no indented lines. This is unrelated to the design document.\\n\\nThe design.md for AR-025 has been written to `/changes/AR-025/design.md` covering:\\n\\n- **Overview**: Three components (AgentMetadata, MetadataOptions, MetadataService)\\n- **Architecture**: Data flow diagram, package layout, dependencies (no new deps)\\n- **Component Design**: Full API specs for all 3 classes with field tables, validators, serialization patterns\\n- **Data Flow Details**: Pack command flow, Build/Publish/Invoke/Status flows, YAML format examples\\n- **Error Handling**: Error matrix with types, messages, and raising components\\n- **Testing Strategy**: Test coverage matrix, fixtures, mock strategy, gate requirements\\n- **Implementation Notes**: 10 design decisions explaining location choices, merge strategies, default conventions, and integration points\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775859688744,\"end\":1775859688744}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-025_ST-2.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775859231027,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2868aa26cffeZQWLM5XkOB8qBZ\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d797564e7001xYOFi8f5jrRpho\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79755e7b001wWs49k26jqoQFP\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2868aa26cffeZQWLM5XkOB8qBZ\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_1cb03e43a27647f089e24cc9\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/.sdd_prompt.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/.sdd_prompt.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: Write delta-spec.md (GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios) for the agentcube project:\\n2: \\n3: AR: AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型\\n4: Module: cmd/cli\\n5: Language: Python\\n6: Size: M\\n7: \\n8: Base specs:\\n9: --- cli-toolkit/design.md ---\\n10: # AgentCube CLI (cli-toolkit) — Design\\n11: \\n12: Source root: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/cmd/cli/`.\\n13: \\n14: ## Package layout (every module path and role)\\n15: \\n16: | Path | Role |\\n17: |------|------|\\n18: | `pyproject.toml` | Project metadata, dependencies, console script mapping |\\n19: | `agentcube/__init__.py` | Package version `__version__`, exports `app`, runtimes |\\n20: | `agentcube/cli/__init__.py` | CLI subpackage marker |\\n21: | `agentcube/cli/main.py` | Typer `app`, all commands, `_handle_error`, `version_callback` |\\n22: | `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | `MetadataOptions` dataclass |\\n23: | `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` | Re-exports runtimes + `MetadataOptions` |\\n24: | `agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py` | `PackRuntime` |\\n25: | `agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` | `BuildRuntime` |\\n26: | `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | `PublishRuntime` |\\n27: | `agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py` | `InvokeRuntime` |\\n28: | `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` | `StatusRuntime` |\\n29: | `agentcube/services/__init__.py` | Services package docstring |\\n30: | `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | `AgentMetadata`, `Metad...\n  Line 11: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775859319241,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2868aa26cffeZQWLM5XkOB8qBZ\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7975d7ef001r80U3vIaGnhBk5\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7975b64a001VPFuhMjdQxIy1y\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2868aa26cffeZQWLM5XkOB8qBZ\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Now I have the full context. Let me write the delta-spec.md for AR-025:\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775859319240,\"end\":1775859319240}}}\n  Line 12: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775859319246,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2868aa26cffeZQWLM5XkOB8qBZ\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7975d941001DtThwGOaemGuVb\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7975b64a001VPFuhMjdQxIy1y\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2868aa26cffeZQWLM5XkOB8qBZ\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"call_b5d0a39671a241c9b10961d8\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型 Delta Spec\\n\\n## Requirement: MetadataService.load_metadata\\nThe system SHALL load agent metadata from a workspace directory, trying `agent_metadata.yaml` first, then falling back to `agent.yaml` and `metadata.yaml`.\\n\\n#### Scenario: Load from primary file\\n- **GIVEN** `{workspace}/agent_metadata.yaml` exists with valid YAML content\\n- **WHEN** `MetadataService.load_metadata(workspace_path)` is called\\n- **THEN** the system SHALL parse the YAML, construct an `AgentMetadata` instance via Pydantic validation, and return it\\n\\n#### Scenario: Fallback to agent.yaml\\n- **GIVEN** `agent_metadata.yaml` does not exist but `{workspace}/agent.yaml` exists\\n- **WHEN** `MetadataService.load_metadata(workspace_path)` is called\\n- **THEN** the system SHALL load and parse `agent.yaml` and return the validated `AgentMetadata` instance\\n\\n#### Scenario: Fallback to metadata.yaml\\n- **GIVEN** neither `agent_metadata.yaml` nor `agent.yaml` exists but `{workspace}/metadata.yaml` exists\\n- **WHEN** `MetadataService.load_metadata(workspace_path)` is called\\n- **THEN** the system SHALL load and parse `metadata.yaml` and return the validated `AgentMetadata` instance\\n\\n#### Scenario: No metadata file found\\n- **GIVEN** none of `agent_metadata.yaml`, `agent.yaml`, or `metadata.yaml` exist in the workspace\\n- **WHEN** `MetadataService.load_metadata(workspace_path)` is called\\n- **THEN** the system SHALL return an `AgentMetadata` instance with default values (language=`\\\"python\\\"`, port=`8080`, build_mode=`\\\"local\\\"`) and required fields unset (raising Pydantic validation errors if accessed without defaults)\\n\\n#### Scenari...\n  Line 15: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775859392175,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2868aa26cffeZQWLM5XkOB8qBZ\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7976d4090017KSiXL3O7hnB0H\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7976c1ff001yGP0ab7bM8K4xu\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2868aa26cffeZQWLM5XkOB8qBZ\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"call_96b79170902843c9bd68d9e6\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型 Delta Spec\\n\\n## Requirement: MetadataService.load_metadata\\nThe system SHALL load agent metadata from a workspace directory, trying `agent_metadata.yaml` first, then falling back to `agent.yaml` and `metadata.yaml`.\\n\\n#### Scenario: Load from primary file\\n- **GIVEN** `{workspace}/agent_metadata.yaml` exists with valid YAML content\\n- **WHEN** `MetadataService.load_metadata(workspace_path)` is called\\n- **THEN** the system SHALL parse the YAML, construct an `AgentMetadata` instance via Pydantic validation, and return it\\n\\n#### Scenario: Fallback to agent.yaml\\n- **GIVEN** `agent_metadata.yaml` does not exist but `{workspace}/agent.yaml` exists\\n- **WHEN** `MetadataService.load_metadata(workspace_path)` is called\\n- **THEN** the system SHALL load and parse `agent.yaml` and return the validated `AgentMetadata` instance\\n\\n#### Scenario: Fallback to metadata.yaml\\n- **GIVEN** neither `agent_metadata.yaml` nor `agent.yaml` exists but `{workspace}/metadata.yaml` exists\\n- **WHEN** `MetadataService.load_metadata(workspace_path)` is called\\n- **THEN** the system SHALL load and parse `metadata.yaml` and return the validated `AgentMetadata` instance\\n\\n#### Scenario: No metadata file found\\n- **GIVEN** none of `agent_metadata.yaml`, `agent.yaml`, or `metadata.yaml` exist in the workspace\\n- **WHEN** `MetadataService.load_metadata(workspace_path)` is called\\n- **THEN** the system SHALL return an `AgentMetadata` instance with default values (language=`\\\"python\\\"`, port=`8080`, build_mode=`\\\"local\\\"`) and required fields unset (raising Pydantic validation errors if accessed without defaults)\\n\\n#### Scenari...\n  Line 18: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775859395744,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2868aa26cffeZQWLM5XkOB8qBZ\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7977e7c8001iFEncHb8pSZgc5\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7977df16001VY7pWeh24PwEfN\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2868aa26cffeZQWLM5XkOB8qBZ\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"glob\",\"callID\":\"call_d34b672d6bae4630963b8ddb\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"delta-spec.md\",\"path\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z\"},\"output\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-025/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-024/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-022/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-021/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_