stance SHALL have defaults `language=\\\"python\\\"`, `port=8080`, `build_mode=\\\"local\\\"`, `requirements_file=\\\"requirements.txt\\\"`, `registry_url=\\\"\\\"`, `registry_username=\\\"\\\"`, `registry_password=\\\"\\\"`, and all `Optional` fields as `None`\\n\\n#### Scenario: Construct with all fields\\n- **GIVEN** a complete dict of all `AgentMetadata` fields\\n- **WHEN** `AgentMetadata(**fields)` is constructed\\n- **THEN** the instance SHALL have all fields set to the provided values\\n\\n#### Scenario: Required field agent_name missing\\n- **GIVEN** no `agent_name` is provided\\n- **WHEN** `AgentMetadata(entrypoint=\\\"main.py\\\")` is constructed\\n- **THEN** Pydantic SHALL raise `ValidationError` for missing required field `agent_name`\\n\\n#### Scenario: Required field entrypoint missing\\n- **GIVEN** no `entrypoint` is provided\\n- **WHEN** `AgentMetadata(agent_name=\\\"test\\\")` is constructed\\n- **THEN** Pydantic SHALL raise `ValidationError` for missing required field `entrypoint`\\n\\n#### Scenario:...\n  Line 30: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775859475633,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2868aa26cffeZQWLM5XkOB8qBZ\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79781a320015NQ7sw19hzsvFa\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79780ece001x6emi1xCxznpqd\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2868aa26cffeZQWLM5XkOB8qBZ\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Now I understand the format. Let me write the delta-spec for AR-025:\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775859475631,\"end\":1775859475631}}}\n  Line 33: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775859483191,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2868aa26cffeZQWLM5XkOB8qBZ\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79792d3c001BF46dnI4MQfQ37\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d797924e4001PyVevlQ8n81cj8\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2868aa26cffeZQWLM5XkOB8qBZ\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Written `changes/AR-025/delta-spec.md` with 10 requirements and 45 acceptance scenarios covering:\\n\\n- **AgentMetadata** Pydantic model (constructors, validators for language/build_mode/port, required fields, defaults)\\n- **MetadataOptions** dataclass (`from_options` with full/partial/empty/unknown-key dicts)\\n- **MetadataService.load_metadata** (primary file, 2 fallbacks, no-file defaults, YAML parse error, Pydantic validation error, verbose logging)\\n- **MetadataService.save_metadata** (YAML formatting, exclude_none, overwrite, verbose logging)\\n- **MetadataService.update_metadata** (existing fields, new fields, invalid rejection, no-existing-creates-new, verbose logging)\\n- **MetadataService.validate_workspace** (valid dir, missing, file-not-dir)\\n- **MetadataService._validate_python_workspace** (py files present, missing raises ValueError)\\n- **MetadataService._validate_java_workspace** (pom.xml present/missing)\\n- **Metadata file format** (structure, nested fields, field order, round-trip consistency)\\n- **File changes** table with target files and test files\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775859483189,\"end\":1775859483189}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-025_ST-1.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775859082064,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2868ce86affePxqVbkjfhLn59M\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79731efd001uVaAr7zkAj7Y4N\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79731886001ytxNYJsZDEtUKB\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2868ce86affePxqVbkjfhLn59M\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_72c4575924324d4190307f1d\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/.sdd_prompt.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/.sdd_prompt.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: Write proposal.md for the agentcube project:\\n2: \\n3: AR: AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型\\n4: Module: cmd/cli\\n5: Language: Python\\n6: Size: M\\n7: \\n8: Relevant specs:\\n9: --- cli-toolkit/design.md ---\\n10: # AgentCube CLI (cli-toolkit) — Design\\n11: \\n12: Source root: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/cmd/cli/`.\\n13: \\n14: ## Package layout (every module path and role)\\n15: \\n16: | Path | Role |\\n17: |------|------|\\n18: | `pyproject.toml` | Project metadata, dependencies, console script mapping |\\n19: | `agentcube/__init__.py` | Package version `__version__`, exports `app`, runtimes |\\n20: | `agentcube/cli/__init__.py` | CLI subpackage marker |\\n21: | `agentcube/cli/main.py` | Typer `app`, all commands, `_handle_error`, `version_callback` |\\n22: | `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | `MetadataOptions` dataclass |\\n23: | `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` | Re-exports runtimes + `MetadataOptions` |\\n24: | `agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py` | `PackRuntime` |\\n25: | `agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` | `BuildRuntime` |\\n26: | `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | `PublishRuntime` |\\n27: | `agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py` | `InvokeRuntime` |\\n28: | `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` | `StatusRuntime` |\\n29: | `agentcube/services/__init__.py` | Services package docstring |\\n30: | `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | `AgentMetadata`, `MetadataService` |\\n31: | `agen...\n  Line 7: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775859136143,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2868ce86affePxqVbkjfhLn59M\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7973513e001XhXJ6NCrpk4unA\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d797323b2001iLkEMJBmmopBbl\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2868ce86affePxqVbkjfhLn59M\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"call_17ddf3b256f9450992feceb1\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-025: MetadataService 与数据模型\\n\\n## 概述\\n\\n为 AgentCube CLI (`cmd/cli`) 设计并实现元数据服务层与核心数据模型，提供 workspace 元数据的加载、保存、验证和更新能力，支撑 `pack`、`build`、`publish`、`invoke`、`status` 全生命周期的元数据管理。\\n\\n## 问题陈述\\n\\nCLI 工具需要在 workspace 目录中持久化 agent 配置信息（语言、入口、端口、镜像、端点等），并在各命令间共享。当前缺乏：\\n\\n1. 统一的元数据模型定义与校验\\n2. 可靠的 YAML 持久化与多文件名回退加载\\n3. 可复用的 MetadataService 供各 Runtime 类调用\\n4. CLI 选项到元数据的合并覆盖机制\\n\\n## 设计方案\\n\\n### 数据模型\\n\\n#### AgentMetadata（Pydantic BaseModel）\\n\\n作为元数据的核心模型，定义在 `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`：\\n\\n| 字段 | 类型 | 默认值 | 说明 |\\n|------|------|--------|------|\\n| `agent_name` | `str` | 必填 | Agent 唯一标识 |\\n| `description` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | 人类可读描述 |\\n| `language` | `str` | `\\\"python\\\"` | 编程语言（python/java） |\\n| `entrypoint` | `str` | 必填 | 启动命令 |\\n| `port` | `int` | `8080` | 暴露端口（1-65535） |\\n| `build_mode` | `str` | `\\\"local\\\"` | 构建策略（local/cloud） |\\n| `region` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | 部署区域 |\\n| `version` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | 语义化版本 |\\n| `image` | `Optional[Dict[str, Any]]` | `None` | 容器镜像信息 |\\n| `auth` | `Optional[Dict[str, Any]]` | `None` | 认证配置 |\\n| `requirements_file` | `Optional[str]` | `\\\"requirements.txt\\\"` | Python 依赖文件 |\\n| `registry_url` | `Optional[str]` | `\\\"\\\"` | 镜像仓库 URL |\\n| `registry_username` | `Optional[str]` | `\\\"\\\"` | 仓库用户名 |\\n| `registry_password` | `Optional[str]` | `\\\"\\\"` | 仓库密码 |\\n| `agent_endpoint` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | Agent 端点 URL |\\n| `workload_manager_url` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | Workload Manager URL |\\n| `router_url` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | Router URL |\\n| `readiness_probe_path` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | 就绪探针路径 |\\n| `readiness_probe_port` | `Optional[int]` | `None` | 就绪探针端口 ...\n  Line 10: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775859139746,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2868ce86affePxqVbkjfhLn59M\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7973ffa4001Qce6NqKnv5crIR\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7973f6ff001Jac71VcuKKXuRE\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2868ce86affePxqVbkjfhLn59M\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"glob\",\"callID\":\"call_30101f38478645118e9abd35\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"**/proposal.md\",\"path\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z\"},\"output\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-025/proposal.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md\\n