ive error handling.\\n\\n## Architecture\\n\\n### Component Diagram\\n\\n```\\n┌─────────────┐\\n│   CLI (Typer)   │\\n│  main.py     │\\n└──────┬──────┘\\n       │ build()\\n       ▼\\n┌─────────────────────┐\\n│  BuildRuntime       │\\n│  build_runtime.py   │\\n└──────┬──────────────┘\\n       │\\n       ├──► MetadataService\\n       │    └── load_metadata()\\n       │    └── save_metadata()\\n       │\\n       └──► DockerService\\n            └── check_docker_available()\\n            └── build_image()\\n            └── get_image_info()\\n```\\n\\n### Key Components\\n\\n1. **CLI Layer** (`agentcube/cli/main.py`)\\n   - Typer command definition\\n   - User input validation\\n   - Error handling and user feedback\\n\\n2. **Runtime Layer** (`agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py`)\\n   - Build orchestration\\n   - Version management\\n   - Build mode selection\\n\\n3. **Service Layer**\\n   - `MetadataService`: Metadata persistence and loading\\n   - `DockerService`: Docker operations (build, push, etc.)\\n\\n## Data Structures\\n\\n### BuildOptions\\n\\nDictionary containing build command options:\\n\\n```python\\n{\\n    \\\"proxy\\\": Optional[str],          # Proxy URL for dependency resolution\\n    \\\"cloud_provider\\\": Optional[str], # Cloud provider name (e.g., \\\"huawei\\\")\\n    \\\"output\\\": Optional[st...\n  Line 40: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775866454279,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2861e289bffeEA9L147U2ruOXd\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79e3a0e3001FpbN7TM0qVdlrr\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79e390dc0011TuiN4plaqkGCZ\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2861e289bffeEA9L147U2ruOXd\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-3788b269d70f43bc827b36f0a4f224bb\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/cmd/cli/design.md\",\"limit\":50},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T16312