期支持\\n29: - **可验证性**: 语言特定工作区验证\\n30: \\n31: ---\\n32: \\n33: ## Scope\\n34: \\n35: ### In-Scope\\n36: \\n37: | Component | Path | Description |\\n38: |-----------|------|-------------|\\n39: | AgentMetadata | `agentcube/models/agent_models.py` | 新的独立模型文件 |\\n40: | MetadataOptions | `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | 增强的方法 |\\n41: | MetadataService | `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | 新增方法 |\\n42: | Unit tests | `tests/test_metadata_service.py` | 测试覆盖 |\\n43: \\n44: ### Out-of-Scope\\n45: \\n46: - CLI 命令参数变更\\n47: - Runtime 类修改\\n48: - 数据库持久化\\n49: \\n50: ---\\n51: \\n52: ## Impact Analysis\\n53: \\n54: ### Dependencies\\n55: \\n56: | Dependency | Purpose | Status |\\n57: |------------|---------|--------|\\n58: | `pydantic>=2.0.0` | 数据模型验证 | ...\n  Line 9: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775866166234,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28620f443ffeOwB10PccdNhCR2\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79df2ff200182iwhEsV3XHYuI\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79df1d13001aFIJTQnx7NkUmq\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28620f443ffeOwB10PccdNhCR2\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_343a0b67ef06441d8103f2b8\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/delta-spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/delta-spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # Delta Spec: AR-020 — CLI pack 命令\\n2: \\n3: ## Overview\\n4: \\n5: This delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the CLI pack command in the AgentCube CLI tool (`kubectl-agentcube`).\\n6: \\n7: ## Base Specifications\\n8: \\n9: - **AR**: AR-020\\n10: - **Module**: `cmd/cli`\\n11: - **Language**: Python\\n12: - **Size**: M\\n13: \\n14: ---\\n15: \\n16: ## Background\\n17: \\n18: The `pack` command is the first step in the AgentCube workflow. It validates the workspace structure, loads or creates agent metadata, processes dependencies, optionally generates a Dockerfile, and prepares the workspace for subsequent build and publish steps.\\n19: \\n20: ---\\n21: \\n22: ## Requirements\\n23: \\n24: ### AR-020-001: Workspace validation\\n25: \\n26: The system SHALL validate that the workspace path exists and contains valid agent source files based on the specified language.\\n27: \\n28: #### Scenario: AR-020-001-A — Valid Python workspace\\n29: \\n30: - **GIVEN** a workspace directory exists at the specified path\\n31: - **WHEN** `pack` is executed with a Python agent (default language)\\n32: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL validate that at least one `*.py` file exists in the workspace root\\n33: - **AND** the workspace SHALL be considered valid for packaging\\n34: \\n35: #### Scenario: AR-020-001-B — Valid Java workspace\\n36: \\n37: - **GIVEN** a workspace directory exists at ...\n  Line 11: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775866166240,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28620f443ffeOwB10PccdNhCR2\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79df3392001LjI8I6OSaJ0q5D\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79df1d13001aFIJTQnx7NkUmq\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28620f443ffeOwB10PccdNhCR2\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_8f7fa8bee82e4bd1b150c1ad\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: \\\"\\\"\\\"Metadata service for AgentCube - handles agent metadata loading, saving, and validation.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n2: \\n3: from __future__ import annotations\\n4: \\n5: import os\\n6: from pathlib import Path\\n7: from typing import Any, Dict, Optional\\n8: \\n9: import yaml\\n10: from pydantic import BaseModel, Field, field_validator\\n11: \\n12: \\n13: class AgentMetadata(Base