ent configuration stored in YAML files) throughout the agent lifecycle: pack, build, publish, invoke, and status operations. This includes loading, saving, updating, and validating metadata based on workspace structure and deployment requirements.\\n20: \\n21: Key components:\\n22: - `AgentMetadata`: Pydantic model for agent configuration\\n23: - `MetadataOptions`: CLI options dataclass for pack operations\\n24: - `MetadataService`: Service class for metadata CRUD operations\\n25: \\n26: ---\\n27: \\n28: ## Requirements\\n29: \\n30: ### Requirement: AgentMetadata model validation\\n31: \\n32: The system SHALL validate `AgentMetadata` fields using Pydantic validators for language, build_mode, and port range.\\n33: \\n34: #### Scenario: Invalid language value\\n35: - **GIVEN** the metadata contains `languag...\n  Line 10: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775866087691,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286223411ffeKbA8FUsl45wcDy\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79de055d001voyWBZXtPEDxIS\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79ddf499001GBWMAR9PYnLiR7\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286223411ffeKbA8FUsl45wcDy\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_b3213eb8d75e4138829af604\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/cli-toolkit/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/cli-toolkit/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AgentCube CLI (cli-toolkit) — Pack Command Design\\n2: \\n3: - **AR ID**: AR-020\\n4: - **Module**: cmd/cli\\n5: - **Language**: Python\\n6: - **Size**: M\\n7: - **Status**: ST-1 Completed (design.md)\\n8: \\n9: ## 1. Overview\\n10: \\n11: ### 1.1 Purpose\\n12: \\n13: The `pack` command is the first step in the AgentCube agent lifecycle workflow. It validates the workspace structure, loads or creates agent metadata, processes dependencies, optionally generates a Dockerfile, and prepares the workspace for subsequent build and publish steps.\\n14: \\n15: ### 1.2 Position in Workflow\\n16: \\n17: ```\\n18: ┌─────────┐    ┌─────────┐    ┌──────────┐    ┌─────────┐\\n19: │  pack   │───▶│  build  │───▶│ publish  │───▶│ invoke  │\\n20: └─────────┘    └─────────┘    └──────────┘    └─────────┘\\n21:      │                                                   │\\n22:      └───────────────────▶ status ◀─────────────────────┘\\n23: ```\\n24: \\n25: ### 1.3 Package Structure\\n26: \\n27: Source root: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/cmd/cli/`\\n28: \\n29: | Path | Role |\\n30: |------|------|\\n31: | `pyproject.toml` | Project metadata, dependencies, console script mapping |\\n32: | `agentcube/__init__.py` | Package version `__version__`, exports `app`, runtimes |\\n33: | `agentcube/cli/__init__.py` | CLI subpackage marker |\\n34: | `agentcube/cli/main.py` | Typer `app`, all commands, `_h...\n  Line 13: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775866095133,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286223411ffeKbA8FUsl45wcDy\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79de217b001O2K4p0OsJcRQCg\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79de0940001MbGCRWhNNUZ9S1\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286223411ffeKbA8FUsl45wcDy\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_df56d4f7a6fb49fbbe6619b3\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: \\\"\\\"\\\"Metadata service for AgentCube - handles agent metadata loading, saving, and validation.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n2: \\n3: from __future__ import annotations\\n4: \\n5: import os\\n6: from pathlib import Path\\n7: from typing import Any, Dict, Optional\\n8: \\n9: import yaml\\n10: from pydantic import BaseModel, Field, field_validator\\n11: \\n12: \\n13: class AgentMetadata(BaseModel):\\n14:     \\\"\\\"\\\"Pydantic model for agent metadata configuration.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n15: \\n16:     agent_name: str = Field(..., description=\\\"Unique name identifying the agent\\\")\\n17:     description: Optional[str] = Field(default=None, description=\\\"Human-readable summary\\\")\\n18:     language: str = Field(default=\\\"python\\\", description=\\\"Programming language used\\\")\\n19:     entrypoint: str = Field(..., description=\\\"Command to launch the agent\\\")\\n20:     port: int = Field(default=8080, description=\\\"Port exposed by the agent runtime\\\")\\n21:     build_mode: str = Field(default=\\\"local\\\", description=\\\"Build strategy: local or cloud\\\")\\n22:     region: Optional[str] = Field(default=None, description=\\\"Deployment region\\\")\\n23:     version: Optional[str] = Field(\\n24:         default=None, description=\\\"Semantic version string for publishing\\\"\\n25:     )\\n26:     image: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = Field(default=None, description=\\\"Container image infor...\n  Line 16: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775866100176,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286223411ffeKbA8FUsl45wcDy\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79de361e001IG1Z7ZV48Lt7oK\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79de2663001h8mvA4ab3fb4z8\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286223411ffeKbA8FUsl45wcDy\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_5b578d7aa4184c57be826cb5\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/tests/test_metadata_service.py\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/tests/test_metadata_service.py</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: \\\"\\\"\\\"Unit tests for MetadataService.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n2: \\n3: import tempfile\\n4: from pathlib import Path\\n5: \\n6: import pytest\\n7: import yaml\\n8: \\n9: from agentcube.ser