ilian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-025/tasks.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型 Tasks\\n2: \\n3: **Module:** cmd/cli  \\n4: **Language:** Python  \\n5: **Size:** M  \\n6: **Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\\n7: \\n8: ---\\n9: \\n10: ## Implementation Tasks\\n11: \\n12: ### Phase 1: AgentMetadata Model Enhancements\\n13: \\n14: - [ ] **T001** Review existing `AgentMetadata` Pydantic model in `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\\n15:   - Verify all fields from design are present\\n16:   - Confirm validators: `validate_language`, `validate_build_mode`, `validate_port`\\n17: \\n18: - [ ] **T002** Write unit tests for `AgentMetadata` validators:\\n19:   - Test invalid language value raises ValidationError\\n20:   - Test invalid build_mode value raises ValidationError\\n21:   - Test port out of range (1-65535) raises ValidationError\\n22:   - Test language normalization (uppercase to lowercase)\\n23: \\n24: - [ ] **T003** Run existing tests to verify current implementation:\\n25:   - `pytest tests/test_metadata_service.py -v`\\n26: \\n27: ---\\n28: \\n29: ### Phase 2: MetadataService Load Operations\\n30: \\n31: - [ ] **T010** Verify existing `load_metadata` fallback chain:\\n32:   - `agent_metadata.yaml` (primary)\\n33:   - `agent.yaml` (fallback)\\n34:   - `metadata.yaml` (fallback)\\n35: \\n36: - [ ] **T011** Verify error handling:\\n37:   - Test `FileNotFoundError` when no metadata file exists\\n38: \\n39: -...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z_logs/AR-021_ST-1.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775866009232,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2862331b3ffe5C04t62J83Vbh5\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79dcd6510014Us3PIx0q4rLUN\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79dccf45001Qhrjzmn4CBU6DF\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2862331b3ffe5C04t62J83Vbh5\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-da1a553c1d5647039ad34d90248baa69\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/.sdd_prompt.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/.sdd_prompt.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: Write proposal.md for the agentcube project:\\n2: \\n3: AR: AR-021 — CLI build 命令\\n4: Module: cmd/cli\\n5: Language: Python\\n6: Size: M\\n7: \\n8: Relevant specs:\\n9: --- cli-toolkit/design.md ---\\n10: # AgentCube CLI (cli-toolkit) — Design\\n11: \\n12: Source root: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/cmd/cli/`.\\n13: \\n14: ## Package layout (every module path and role)\\n15: \\n16: | Path | Role |\\n17: |------|------|\\n18: | `pyproject.toml` | Project metadata, dependencies, console script mapping |\\n19: | `agentcube/__init__.py` | Package version `__version__`, exports `app`, runtimes |\\n20: | `agentcube/cli/__init__.py` | CLI subpackage marker |\\n21: | `agentcube/cli/main.py` | Typer `app`, all commands, `_handle_error`, `version_callback` |\\n22: | `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | `MetadataOptions` dataclass |\\n23: | `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` | Re-exports runtimes + `MetadataOptions` |\\n24: | `agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py` | `PackRuntime` |\\n25: | `agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` | `BuildRuntime` |\\n26: | `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | `PublishRuntime` |\\n27: | `agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py` | `InvokeRuntime` |\\n28: | `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` | `StatusRuntime` |\\n29: | `agentcube/services/__init__.py` | Services package docstring |\\n30: | `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | `AgentMetadata`, `MetadataService` |...\n  Line 13: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775866124062,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2862331b3ffe5C04t62J83Vbh5\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79de9622001B2ZegHya10igvN\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79dd1344001DH3Fr1sy1EMhbJ\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2862331b3ffe5C04t62J83Vbh5\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-19345c8366614ff4beb3b9a340c3b841\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-021: CLI build 命令\\n\\n## Overview\\n\\n实现 AgentCube CLI 的 `build` 命令，用于从打包好的工作空间构建容器镜像。该命令支持本地 Docker 构建和云端构建两种模式，能够自动管理版本号、验证构建前置条件，并集成 Docker 服务进行镜像构建。\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\n提供 `kubectl-agentcube build` 命令，实现：\\n\\n1. **本地 Docker 构建**：使用本地 Docker 守护进程构建容器镜像\\n2. **云端构建**：集成云服务商（如华为云）的构建服务\\n3. **版本管理**：自动递增版本号（patch 级别），构建失败时回滚版本\\n4. **代理支持**：支持自定义代理 URL 进行依赖解析\\n5. **构建结果输出**：输出镜像名称、ID、大小等构建信息\\n6. **元数据更新**：更新 `agent_metadata.yaml` 中的构建信息\\n\\n## Module\\n\\n`cmd/cli` - AgentCube CLI 工具包\\n\\n## Language\\n\\nPython 3.10+\\n\\n## Size\\n\\nM\\n\\n## Scope\\n\\n### In Scope\\n\\n1. **BuildRuntime 类实现** (`agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py`)\\n   - `build()` 主方法，支持本地和云端构建模式\\n   - `_increment_version()` - 版本号递增逻辑\\n   - `_validate_build_prerequisites()` - 构建前置条件验证\\n   - `_build_local()` - 本地 Docker 构建\\n   - `_build_cloud()` - 云端构建（华为云等）\\n   - `_update_build_metadata()` - 更新构建元数据\\n\\n2. **CLI 命令集成** (`agentcube/cli/main.py`)\\n   - `build()` Typer 命令函数\\n   - 命令行参数：`--workspace`, `--proxy`, `--cloud-provider`, `--output`, `--verbose`\\n   - 错误处理和用户反馈\\n\\n3. **Docker 服务集成** (`agentcube/services/docker_service.py`)\\n   - `build_image()` - 构建镜像方法\\n   - 支持构建参数（buildargs）\\n   - 支持代理配置\\n   - 返回镜像信息（名称、ID、大小、构建时间）\\n\\n4. **元数据服务集成** (`agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`)\\n   - 加载和保存 `agent_metadata.yaml`\\n   - 版本管理\\n   - 构建结果持久化\\n\\n### Out of Scope\\n\\n- Docker 守护进程安装和配置\\n- 云服务提供商 SDK 实现（使用已有 SDK）\\n- Dockerfile 生成（由 `pack` 命令完成）\\n- 镜像推送功能（由 `publish` 命令完成）\\n\\n## Impact Analysis\\n\\n### Components Impacted\\n\\n1. **CLI 工具包** (`cmd/cli`)\\n   - 添加 `build` 命令到 Typer 应用\\n   - 新增 `BuildRuntime` 类\\n   - 更新导入和依赖\\n\\n2. **Docker 服务** (`agentcube/services/docker_s...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z_logs/AR-025_ST-3.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775865968213,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28623daf0ffez95ulaFqw2gZJI\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79dc3214001xADPaypc1vjyE0\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79dc25f4001SqS2RHyFUeAyZ8\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28623daf0ffez95ulaFqw2gZJI\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_b8aa6ece12974579a1748c42\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/.sdd_prompt.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/.sdd_prompt.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: Write design.md with technical implementation details for the agentcube project:\\n2: \\n3: AR: AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型\\n4: Module: cmd/cli\\n5: Language: Python\\n6: Size: M\\n7: \\n8: Specs:\\n9: --- cli-toolkit/design.md ---\\n10: # AgentCube CLI (cli-toolkit) — Design\\n11: \\n12: Source root: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/cmd/cli/`.\\n13: \\n14: ## Package layout (every module path and role)\\n15: \\n16: | Path | Role |\\n17: |------|------|\\n18: | `pyproject.toml` | Project metadata, dependencies, console script mapping |\\n19: | `agentcube/__init__.py` | Package version `__version__`, exports `app`, runtimes |\\n20: | `agentcube/cli/__init__.py` | CLI subpackage marker |\\n21: | `agentcube/cli/main.py` | Typer `app`, all commands, `_handle_error`, `version_callback` |\\n22: | `agentcube/models/pack_models.py` | `MetadataOptions` dataclass |\\n23: | `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` | Re-exports runtimes + `MetadataOptions` |\\n24: | `agentcube/runtime/pack_runtime.py` | `PackRuntime` |\\n25: | `agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` | `BuildRuntime` |\\n26: | `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | `PublishRuntime` |\\n27: | `agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py` | `InvokeRuntime` |\\n28: | `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` | `StatusRuntime` |\\n29: | `agentcube/services/__init__.py` | Se