idators for language, build_mode, and port range.\\n\\n#### Scenario: Invalid language value\\n- **GIVEN** the metadata contains `language` set to `\\\"javascript\\\"`\\n- **WHEN** Pydantic validates the model\\n- **THEN** it SHALL raise a `ValidationError` with message indicating allowed values are `['python', 'java']`\\n\\n#### Scenario: Invalid build_mode value\\n- **GIVEN** the metadata contains `build_mode` set to `\\\"hybrid\\\"`\\n- **WHEN** Pydantic validates the model\\n- **THEN** it SHALL raise a `ValidationError` with message indicating allowed values are `['local', 'cloud']`\\n...\n  Line 26: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775865961691,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28625b516ffeco0EXVAT8d2Aa3\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79dc1262001iIHc2LvsaYe58W\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79dc0169001a4yqRYFb8xcRzk\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28625b516ffeco0EXVAT8d2Aa3\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"已完成 `delta-spec.md` 的编写，涵盖以下场景：\\n\\n1. **AgentMetadata 模型验证** - 语言、构建模式、端口范围验证器\\n2. **MetadataService 加载操作** - 主文件加载 + 回退机制 (agent_metadata.yaml → agent.yaml → metadata.yaml)\\n3. **MetadataService 保存操作** - YAML 格式化规则\\n4. **MetadataService 更新操作** - 部分更新 + 重新验证\\n5. **工作区验证** - Python (*.py) 和 Java (pom.xml) 结构验证\\n6. **MetadataOptions 转换** - CLI 选项到数据类的转换及默认值\\n7. **部署字段传播** - AgentRuntime CR 和 Kubernetes 部署所需字段\\n8. **镜像和注册表元数据** - 构建后镜像信息存储\\n9. **会话和代理 ID 跟踪** - 发布后的状态追踪\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775865961689,\"end\":1775865961689}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z_logs/AR-020_ST-6.log:\n  Line 14: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775865789001,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28626b0b1ffehV4WkqbQmoBIjm\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79d97a080012n03L0hmh76IEN\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79d96218001xrTmbakL05JDzH\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28626b0b1ffehV4WkqbQmoBIjm\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-06bb90e9d30845f68b06076e8a8dcffa\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces