` |\\n24: | `agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py` | `Ag...\n  Line 23: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775865284497,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2862e79c9ffeeyo7XEFl77yktq\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79d1c75e001oZGdbkGW7O0QjF\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79d1be50001iEDgU0sARkPJ23\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2862e79c9ffeeyo7XEFl77yktq\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-e96aa15fb9ee434bb7a2b010612d54e9\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/cli-toolkit/spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/cli-toolkit/spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AgentCube CLI (cli-toolkit) Specification\\n2: \\n3: ## Purpose\\n4: \\n5: Command-line tool (`kubectl-agentcube`) for packaging, building, publishing, invoking, and checking status of AI agents against AgentCube or standard Kubernetes.\\n6: \\n7: ## Requirements\\n8: \\n9: ### Requirement: Global CLI options\\n10: The system SHALL expose a Typer application named `agentcube` with global options on the root callback.\\n11: \\n12: #### Scenario: Version display\\n13: - **GIVEN** the CLI is installed and importable\\n14: - **WHEN** the user passes `--version` (eager option, `Optional[bool]`, default `None`)\\n15: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL print `AgentCube CLI (kubectl agentcube) version: {__version__}` (Rich markup) and exit without running a subcommand (`typer.Exit()`), where `__version__` is `0.1.0` from `agentcube.__init__`\\n16: \\n17: #### Scenario: Global verbose logging\\n18: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--verbose` / `-v` (`bool`, default `False`) on the root callback\\n19: - **WHEN** the callback runs\\n20: - **THEN** the system SHALL call `logging.basicConfig(level=logging.DEBUG)`\\n21: \\n22: ### Requirement: `pack` command\\n23: The system SHALL provide `pack` to validate and prepare a workspace, merge CLI overrides into metadata, optionally generate a `Dockerfile`, and report paths.\\n24: \\n25: #### Scenario: Options and defaults\\n26: - **GIVE...\n  Line 57: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775865393703,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2862e79c9ffeeyo7XEFl77yktq\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79d370500013bvs63nxWLgpHL\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79d36032001Ps8qb07qvD2xHd\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2862e79c9ffeeyo7XEFl77yktq\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-4054892802114d69a35ff9e3c3c8cdc7\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"\\\"\\\"\\\"Services package for agentcube CLI.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\\nfrom agentcube.services.metadata_service import MetadataService\\nfrom agentcube.services.docker_service import DockerService\\n\\n__all__ = [\\\"MetadataService\\\", \\\"DockerService\\\"]\",\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/services/__init__.py\"},\"output\":\"Wrote file successfully.\\n\\nLSP errors detected in other files:\\n<diagnostics file=\\\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/server/server.go\\\">\\nERROR [50:27] undefined: store.NewValkeyStore\\n</diagnostics>\\n\\nLSP errors detected in other files:\\n<diagnostics file=\\\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_test.go\\\">\\nERROR [138:50] cannot use mockStore (variable of type *mockStore) as store.Store value in argument to NewSandboxHandler: *mockStore does not implement store.Store (missing method GetSandboxBySessionID)\\nERROR [161:36] cannot use mockStore (variable of type *mockStore) as store.Store value in argument to NewSandboxHandler: *mockStore does not implement store.Store (missing method GetSandboxBySessionID)\\nERROR [181:36] cannot use mockStore (variable of type *mockStore) as store.Store value in ar